---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCTA from '../components/ContactCTA.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | Trever Berryman" description="About | Trever Berryman">
	<div class="stack gap-20">
		<main class="wrapper about">
			<Hero
				title="About"
				tagline=""
			>
				<img
					width="1553"
					height="873"
					src="../../assets/AlienAboutMe.png"
					alt="Cartoon alien illustration representing Trever Berryman"
				/>
			</Hero>

			<section aria-labelledby="background-heading">
				<h2 id="background-heading" class="section-title">Hi, I’m Trever 👋</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<br>
					<ul>
						<li><b>Tier-2 Help Desk</b> professional</li>
						<li><b>Software & Hardware QA Tester</b></li>
						<li><b>Designer</b></li>
						<li>Exploring Automation, DevOps, Open Source, AI/ML, Creative Technology 🧑‍💻</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section aria-labelledby="offerings-heading">
				<h2 id="offerings-heading" class="section-title">Offerings</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li><b>Help Desk Support</b></li>
						<li><b>Non-Profit Operations</b></li>
						<li><b>QA Testing</b></li>
						<li><b>Designing and Developing</b>
							<ul>
								<li>WordPress Website creation</li>
								<li>Personal Website creation</li>
								<li>AI Workflows</li>
								<li>Automation</li>
							</ul>
						</li>
						<li><b>Resume Reviews / Mentorship</b></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section aria-labelledby="skills-heading">
				<h2 id="skills-heading" class="section-title">Skills</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
					  <li><b>Languages:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>C#, JavaScript, HTML5, CSS, No Code Tools</li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					  <li><b>Frameworks &amp; Libraries:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>Astro, WordPress, Electron</li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					  <li><b>Management, DevOps &amp; Deployment:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>Git, Unity DevOps Version Control (Plastic SCM), TeamCity, Perforce, ITIL v4, Command Line Interfaces (CLI), Node.js, NPM </li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					  <li><b>Software:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>PDQ Deploy, Active Directory (AD), Visual Studio Code, JIRA, Test Rail, ConnectWise, Mailchimp, CRMs (Hubspot, etc)</li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					  <li><b>Cloud:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>Microsoft Azure (PlayFab) </li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					  <li><b>Operating Systems:</b>
						<ul>
						  <li>macOS, Windows 11/10/8/7, iOS, Android</li>
						</ul>
					  </li>
					</ul>
				  </div>
				  
			</section>
			<section aria-labelledby="More About Me">
				<h2 id="more-about-me-heading" class="section-title">More About Me</h2>
				<div class="content">
					<ul>
						<li>Professionally, I'm currently interested in automation and CI/CD and I'm learning more about those now.</li>
						<li>Personally, I'm passionate about creative technology and its connection to positive outcomes toward social impact, mental health advocacy, and climate change. I'm an English native, pero estoy practicando Español tambien. I also have studied a little bit of Mandarin Chinese. I'm also an Emoji lover and a natural tinkerer.</li>						
						<li>I love music, please recommend me your favorites! Here's my profile on <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/caliguy225" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Trever's Spotify Profile (opens in new tab)">Spotify↗</a></li>
						<li>Occasionally I make art with photography (mainly nature and street photography) You can see my art <a href="https://treverberryman.notion.site/Trever-s-Photography-Digital-Art-and-AI-Art-e46f59f7c7bc4e57aad64dabf7c7b6b7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Trever's Photography and Digital Art on Notion (opens in new tab)">here↗</a></li>
						<ul>
							<li>I also have <a href="https://www.redbubble.com/people/treverberryman/shop?asc=u" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Trever's Redbubble Store (opens in new tab)">Redbubble</a> and a <a href="https://www.inprnt.com/profile/treverberryman/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Trever's INPRNT Store (opens in new tab)">INPRNT</a> store where I sell my art and designs.</li>
						</ul>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<ContactCTA />
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.about {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3.5rem;
	}

	img {
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--gray-200);
	}

	.section-title {
		grid-column-start: 1;
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		color: var(--gray-0);
	}

	.content {
		grid-column: 2 / 4;
	}

	.content :global(a) {
		text-decoration: 1px solid underline transparent;
		text-underline-offset: 0.25em;
		transition: text-decoration-color var(--theme-transition);
	}

	.content :global(a:hover),
	.content :global(a:focus) {
		text-decoration-color: currentColor;
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.about {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 60% 1fr;
		}

		.about > :global(:first-child) {
			grid-column-start: 2;
		}

		section {
			display: contents;
			font-size: var(--text-lg);
		}
	}
</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const currentPath = window.location.pathname;
    const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-items a');
    navLinks.forEach(link => {
      if(link.getAttribute('href') === currentPath) {
        link.classList.add('active');
        link.setAttribute('aria-current', 'page');
      } else {
        link.classList.remove('active');
        link.removeAttribute('aria-current');
      }
    });
  });
</script>

